(70, 'Feroglobin Liquid 200ml', 'admin', 394, 26, 110, 333, 154, '[\"uploads\\/products\\/photos\\/iYHdb8aXZSHiwIIdharf3RYcIY0v2q7IYtTe1nf5.jpg\"]', 'uploads/products/thumbnail/xqbovjGlYEcY01ViK6T1LUd04kCBnO2gWedo8ECJ.jpg', 'uploads/products/featured/WvmE3lS8KdESL4RHz3UYAS37NtKKv8L7c9YSIhEs.jpg', 'uploads/products/flash_deal/ezlXX5JGLDklVMgPyxrSXdXMKLkfgwsyoaVBzSaD.jpg', 'youtube', NULL, 'Feroglobin Liquid', '20220320', '<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(100, 100, 100); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;\">Gentle iron to help support your haemoglobin and red blood cells</strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(100, 100, 100); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Feroglobin Liquid is a delicious honey and orange flavour liquid iron formula with nutrients to help maintain health and vitality, including folate which contributes to the reduction of tiredness &amp; fatigue. It provides an organic form of iron citrate complex fo